        <abstract> 
<p>Lyell has been strongly urging John Murray to publish CD’s book [<hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>]. JDH feels Lyell overestimates the public interest in such works.</p> 
            <p>Gives examples of plants showing most marked varieties on the edge of their range.</p>
        </abstract>
